parameters: It's been a while... or maybe not.
You didn't fall into that hole and die?
And I only jumped down, I didn't fall in!
So you are safe after all.
That hole actually connects all the way here?
That hole only led to a centipede's nest.
...Does that mean you just... climbed back up?
We have a favor we'd like you to hear, Luora.
Would you please lend us your power?
We just want you to accompany us on our journey.
Ah, so that's what you meant.
I thought we helped you out plenty already.
No, I'd love to go with you if I'm able.
I just thought it was a pity.
I have things to do and places to be.
We have a question we'd like to ask you.
Miss Luora, do you know of the Lord of Reason?
We're looking for someone known by that title──
So if you know anything, it'd be appreciated.
You look different from what I imagined...
She said it'd be easier starting from Ront.
I see, you're on your little world experience trip.
I went through it once, too.
You've traveled around Parlates too, huh?
I then decided to stay in this world.
Both the fact that Miss Luora is a Lord of Reason, and
that an adventurer would choose Parlates over Ordwald.
Adventurers get excited about the unknown, after all.
I understood that, but even Ordwald──
By the way, what do you want from the Lord of Reason?
It was just a good destination we decided on.
I thought I'd be challenged to a fight, at that.
Doesn't a Lord of Reason sound, like, super strong?
The kind that makes you want to fight them?
I hate fighting myself, but in general...
...Right, let's put a plug on that.
Regardless, I'm sorry to be the reason that
But without a goal, we won't be motivated...
How about we go back to the Penis Plan™?
Even if your goal leads you beyond this village...
a place I recommend anyone go to.
Basically, monsters there are really tough.
There's a way around without being found,
Doesn't that mean it's fine regardless?
Even if you don't die, you still feel the pain, right?
And what if you're tortured to the brink of death,
But, if we can't proceed any further, then...
can I ask you for another favor?
I want you to give this to Miss Tahati.
I could go by myself, but it's not a good idea to
It's important, so don't lose it.
This feels like a new goal, but
I suppose our journey on Ront ends here for now...
You're a Reason Lord Candidate, aren't you?
What your planet will look like...
I look forward to seeing it.
She's telling you to become a Lord already.
It's a natural idea for Miss Luora.
You should want to increase Parlates' allies.
But it also means giving up on
the world you lived in, right? Normally,
You don't seem to be feeling well.
A monster that can't talk, maybe?
You dealt with the monsters in the mountains?
But how did you know of that?
The Barbarians come to this village often,
so that might be the case.
Still, isn't it a little too quickly...?
Woof will show you to village chief!
She probably thinks we're already friends.
We can't leave her alone, can we?
Also, she said she'll introduce us to the
Right, she ran to the house in the east.
That's probably where the chief is.
\C[17]Canine Companions\C[0] has been added to the Event List.
You're pretty motivated, but there's probably
But to travel, woof will try.
Then we will do our best to support you.
\C[17]Village Well\C[0] has been added to the Event List.
We can descend downward into this well.
What is at the end of the river, I wonder?
Is this area rich in Mana?
But I can't read it from here.
Is this area rich in Mana?
I come here from the mountains to do business.
You can never have too much Mana.
Wanna buy something before leaving on your trip?
Fufufu... Now, let's go on a journey!
Fufufu... You have to get the chief's permission!
You can't pass here without permission from the chief!
Head southwest of Tantali and you'll find the Mana Ranch.
Especially a pretty boy like you...
but the village chief said to eat vegetables too.
以前に来たときと同じ、平和な雰囲気だね。
ここでも異変が起きてるって言ってたよな？
起きているかもしれない、くらいの意味だったのかも。
ヴァルコさんは様子を確認してほしいとしか
まあ、本当に何かあって助けが必要なら
ルオーラがアイノアに来そうだしな。
……ルオーラさんはどこで何をしているんだろう。
ルオーラさん、不可解な行動をしていたから。
トーリオンでのことを言ってるんだよな？
誰かに命令されてそうな感じだったんだっけ？
それはぼくやカウンさんの予想だけど、
いずれにせよ……違和感がある。
それなら、せっかくロントに来たんだし。
その情報から集めればいいんだよ。
それが私たちの本来の目的だろ？
ぼくたちは理の主を探す旅をしてた……
山の集落に行ってみよう。
山の集落って、蛮族が住んでる村だっけ？
集落の蛮族たちとルオーラさんは、
お互いのことをよく知っている雰囲気だったから。
……つまり、居場所を知ってる蛮族が
いるかもしれねーってことか。
\C[17]大地を覆う影\C[0]'s details have been updated.

今の内にパーラテスのすべてを

住んでる……わけじゃないかな。

なんとなく聞いてみただけだ。
